<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}Salon de Coiffure Luxe{% endblock %}</title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --gold: #FFD700;
            --dark-gold: #DAA520;
            --black: #000000;
            --dark-gray: #1a1a1a;
            --light-gray: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
        }
        
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            background-color: var(--black) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .navbar-brand {
            color: var(--gold) !important;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) !important;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--gold) !important;
        }
        
        .btn-gold {
            background-color: var(--gold);
            color: var(--black);
            border: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .btn-gold:hover {
            background-color: var(--dark-gold);
            color: var(--black);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-black {
            background-color: var(--black);
            color: var(--gold);
            border: 2px solid var(--gold);
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .btn-black:hover {
            background-color: var(--dark-gray);
            color: var(--gold);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .card-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--dark-gray) 100%);
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: var(--black);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            padding: 40px 0 20px;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }
        
        .footer h5 {
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .footer a:hover {
            color: var(--gold);
        }
        
        .badge-gold {
            background-color: var(--gold);
            color: var(--black);
        }
        
        .text-gold {
            color: var(--gold) !important;
        }
        
        .bg-gold {
            background-color: var(--gold) !important;
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--dark-gray) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 0;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 80px;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: var(--gold);
        }
    </style>
    
    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
                <i class="bi bi-scissors"></i> Salon Sana
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
                            <i class="bi bi-house"></i> Accueil
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_services') }}">
                            <i class="bi bi-grid"></i> Services
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_appointment') }}">
                            <i class="bi bi-calendar-check"></i> Rendez-vous
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_contact') }}">
                            <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> Contact
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    {% if is_granted('ROLE_ADMIN') %}
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('admin_dashboard') }}">
                                <i class="bi bi-gear"></i> Admin
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    {% elseif is_granted('ROLE_EMPLOYEE') %}
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('employee_dashboard') }}">
                                <i class="bi bi-briefcase"></i> Employé
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if app.user %}
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">
                                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right"></i> Déconnexion
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    {% else %}
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_login') }}">
                                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right"></i> Connexion
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    {% endif %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Flash Messages -->
    {% for label, messages in app.flashes %}
        {% for message in messages %}
            <div class="alert alert-{{ label }} alert-dismissible fade show mx-3 mt-3" role="alert">
                {{ message }}
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-scissors"></i> Salon Sana</h5>
                    <p>Votre beauté, notre passion. Depuis 2024, nous offrons des services de coiffure de haute qualité.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>Liens Rapides</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">Accueil</a></li>
                        <li><a href="{{ path('app_services') }}">Services</a></li>
                        <li><a href="{{ path('app_appointment') }}">Prendre RDV</a></li>
                        <li><a href="{{ path('app_contact') }}">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>Contact</h5>
                    <p>
                        <i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i> Amal 2, Agadir 80000, Maroc<br>
                        <i class="bi bi-telephone"></i> +212 6 41 86 96 78<br>
                        <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> moumidmounir@gmail.com
                    </p>
                    <div class="social-links mt-3">
                        <a href="#" class="me-3"><i class="bi bi-facebook fs-4"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="me-3"><i class="bi bi-instagram fs-4"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-tiktok fs-4"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="border-color: var(--gold);">
            <div class="text-center">
                <p>&copy; 2024 Salon Sana. Tous droits réservés.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    
    {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>
